{"id":83868,"type":2,"name":"ばらかもん","name_cn":"元气囝仔","date":"2014-07-05","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/95/70/83868_FfaxZ.jpg","rating":{"rank":488,"total":3349,"count":{"1":2,"2":1,"3":6,"4":6,"5":40,"6":210,"7":877,"8":1696,"9":401,"10":110},"score":7.7},"summary":"因缘际会下，来到日本最西端的岛上生活的年轻帅哥书法家·半田清舟。在开始不习惯的乡村生活的“老师”面前，出现了一名天真浪漫的岛上囝仔·奈留……？在都市长大的傲娇老师和胸襟异常宽阔的岛上居民交织而成的触动人心岛屿喜剧！","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>元气囝仔</li><li><span>话数: </span>12</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>2014年7月5日</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>星期六</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/12047\">ヨシノサツキ</a></li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/2956\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">橘正紀</a></li><li><span>脚本: </span><a href=\"/person/14346\">杉浦理史</a></li><li><span>分镜: </span><a href=\"/person/1798\">荒川眞嗣</a>、<a href=\"/person/14760\">かおり</a>、<a href=\"/person/7866\">川面真也</a>、<a href=\"/person/26330\">中村里美</a>、<a href=\"/person/750\">小島正幸</a>、<a href=\"/person/2956\">橘正紀</a></li><li><span>演出: </span><a href=\"/person/2956\">橘正紀</a>、<a href=\"/person/23200\">飯野慎也</a>、<a href=\"/person/15330\">大野和寿</a>、<a href=\"/person/14543\">石川健朝</a>、<a href=\"/person/650\">金子伸吾</a>、<a href=\"/person/7866\">川面真也</a>、<a href=\"/person/26330\">中村里美</a></li><li><span>音乐: </span><a href=\"/person/67\">川井憲次</a></li><li><span>人物设定: </span><a href=\"/person/12523\">まじろ</a></li><li><span>系列构成: </span><a href=\"/person/14346\">杉浦理史</a></li><li><span>美术监督: </span><a href=\"/person/5990\">加藤浩</a></li><li><span>色彩设计: </span><a href=\"/person/3566\">宮脇裕美</a></li><li><span>总作画监督: </span><a href=\"/person/12523\">まじろ</a></li><li><span>作画监督: </span><a href=\"/person/3623\">貞方希久子</a>、<a href=\"/person/40733\">若月愛子</a>、<a href=\"/person/12238\">伊藤秀樹</a>、<a href=\"/person/12252\">松尾亜希子</a>、<a href=\"/person/30113\">澤田美香</a>、<a href=\"/person/30111\">北村晋哉</a>、<a href=\"/person/30438\">伊集院いづろ</a>、<a href=\"/person/36212\">伊藤晋之</a>、<a href=\"/person/11981\">丸山修二</a>、<a href=\"/person/12523\">まじろ</a>、<a href=\"/person/11315\">吉原達矢</a>、<a href=\"/person